      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Well-kept used car in good condition. It starts, runs, and drives well, and overall it has been cared for better than average. Expect a clean, presentable interior and exterior with normal signs of use and some minor cosmetic wear consistent with age, but nothing suggesting a neglected vehicle. A solid choice for someone looking for a dependable used car without paying mint-condition money.",
