      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Full of grit, charm, and second-chance potential, this car is the kind of find that speaks to drivers who appreciate character over perfection. It has the honest, broken-in presence of a vehicle that\u2019s lived a real life and still has more stories left to tell. Whether you\u2019re hunting for a budget-friendly daily, a hands-on project, or a dependable backup with personality, this one offers an affordable entry point and plenty of opportunity to make it your own. A no-frills ride with soul, ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Honest, affordable transportation with solid value for the money. This vehicle shows its age cosmetically, but it offers a practical option for buyers seeking dependable basic driving, a project, or a low-cost second car. Priced to reflect condition while still delivering real utility, this is a straightforward opportunity from a seller committed to clear, trustworthy representation.",
